  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Cholera
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    Vibrio cholerae
Transmission:Contaminated water
Symptoms:    Profuse watery diarrhea, vomiting
Treatment:   Oral rehydration, antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   0.095M
Vaccine:     Yes
Discovered:  1854

Disease:     HIV/AIDS
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    HIV
Transmission:Sexual contact, blood
Symptoms:    Flu-like; then AIDS symptoms
Treatment:   Antiretroviral therapy (ART)
Deaths/yr:   0.65M
Vaccine:     No (in development)
Discovered:  1983

Disease:     Cancer
Type:        Cellular
Pathogen:    Various causes
Transmission:Non-communicable
Symptoms:    Lumps, weight loss, fatigue
Treatment:   Chemo, surgery, immunotherapy
Deaths/yr:   10.0M
Vaccine:     Some (HPV, Hep B vaccines)
Discovered:  Ancient

